improved_metadata.title: Straight Outta the Ass (Comedy Rap)
improved_metadata.description: A comedic hip-hop track filled with ridiculous rhymes and absurd scenarios. The song pokes fun at gangsta rap tropes with silly punchlines.
improved_metadata.key_lyrics: Straight outta the ass, with a gang of crack jokes
